dt-example.info:
This is the searchPanes extension for DataTables. It allows results to be filtered based on the values of columns.

This example shows how to edit the text in the clear and hide show buttons.

new $.fn.dataTable.Buttons(table, {
        buttons: [
            {
                text: 'SearchPane' + idx,
                action(e, dt, node, conf) {
                    this.hidePane(idx);
                }
            }
        ]
    });
